": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/611406898"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI1d2Gz4C7sf9QEAMaCDk4MTQ4OTQyIMSasKUGMAA4gAZAHnIJNjExNDA2ODk4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1689584969.342909", "card_id": "Q_611716184", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 64}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "报告称高学历「打工人」最焦虑，而本科学历「打工人」最抗压，如何看待这一数据？你如何缓解工作焦虑？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "当学历不同时，各年龄段的心理复原力差别较大。我们发现，随着学历的增加，心理复原力呈现出上升水平，而各年龄段大学本科学历的人群心理复原力水平最高，抵御风险的能力最好。 非常有趣的一个现象是，在 18-25 岁的 Z 世代群体中，拥有研究生及以上学历的受访者反而呈现出最低的心理复原力水平，平均分为 25.30。 而 26 岁以上的三个年龄段，都是高中及以下学历的受访者心理复原力水平最低。部分原因可能是，高学历的 Z 世代人群通常刚入职场或是仍在高校中学习，缺乏社会经验的历练。 别怪这届年轻人「玻璃心」| Z 世代职场洞察"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-fc28dd4beba34cefbe78e565532096e2.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/611716184"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I1d2Gz4C7sf9QEAMaCDk4MjE3NjM5IJa8uaUGMAA4gAFAH3IJNjExNzE2MTg0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "32_1689584969.343916", "card_id": "Q_609100012", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 26}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "人为什么会长皱纹？如何科学预防皱纹？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-6b4a8510b783d4474b2bdb566e49008d_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/609100012"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I1d2Gz4C7sf9QEAMaCDk3NjM2MjYxIKq67aQGMAA4N0Agcgk2MDkxMDAwMTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "33_1689584969.344191", "card_id": "Q_609830185", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 33}, "target": {"t